 Experience solving hard analytical problems via quick prototype and test of new ideas, and implementation of cost-effective tradeoffs in large-scale software systems within research and development. 
 Experience leading the development and delivery of high-quality software solutions to develop and operationalize models, tools, and applications that drive optimized decision making. 
 Experience leading teams and deploying solutions in an agile, DevSecOps, CI/CDenvironments using lifecycle management methods and tools. 
 
